# Website Prompts

Version: 1.0

Status: Approved

Owner: Founder

Last Updated: July 2026

Document Type: Prompt Standard

---

# Purpose

This document defines how Artificial Intelligence retrieves and applies official website standards within the BUXA Business Operating System.

Website prompts do not create business knowledge.

They organise existing business knowledge into structured, consistent and customer-focused website content.

The purpose of website prompts is to ensure that every webpage follows the official BUXA Website Standards while strengthening customer understanding and confidence.

---

# Vision

Every AI-generated webpage should feel like a natural extension of the official BUXA website.

Regardless of page type or AI platform, website content should follow one consistent structure, one business philosophy and one customer experience.

Website prompts should transform business knowledge into structured digital experiences.

---

# Website Philosophy

Business knowledge already exists.

Website prompts organise that knowledge.

Artificial Intelligence structures the presentation.

Customers gain understanding.

Understanding builds confidence.

Website prompts should organise knowledge rather than create it.

---

# Website Architecture

Every website interaction follows one consistent framework.

```text
Business Knowledge
        │
        ▼
Website Standards
        │
        ▼
Website Prompt
        │
        ▼
Artificial Intelligence
        │
        ▼
Structured Website Content
        │
